<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.5.8">
<l>yāyum piṟaru maṟiyāta yāmattu</l>
<l>māya valavaippeṇ vantu mulaitara</l>
<l>pēyeṉ ṟavaḷaip piṭittu <supplied>vu</supplied>yiruṇṭa</l>
<l>vāyava ṉēkoṭṭāy cappāṇi</l>
<l rend="indent">mālvaṇṇaṉē koṭṭāy cappāṇi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When a wicked woman, whom I and others did not know,</l>
<l>Coming in disguise in the darkness, gave [you] her breast,</l>
<l>Grabbing her saying, “[She’s] a demon,”</l>
<l>You, whose lips sucked out her life, please clap your hands;</l>
<l rend="indent">dark-hued one, please clap your hands!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
